      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "This car is an absolute gem in showroom condition! It looks and feels brand new, with flawless paint, a spotless interior, and mechanical performance that is simply perfect. If you're looking for a vehicle that has been meticulously preserved and cared for, this is the one for you!",
