    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been reliably maintained throughout its life. While the exterior shows some minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with regular use, the body is straight and free of major dents. Inside, the cabin is clean, though there is some light wear on the driver\u2019s seat bolster and floor mats. Mechanically, the car is in great shape, with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine. It\u2019s a dependable, honest vehicle that offers a great balance of performance and value for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "good",
